data.description: This well maintained townhouse features an updated kitchen with granite countertops and a stylish backsplash. The spacious kitchen has a  breakfast bar that overlooks the spacious living room. There is a separate dining area with access to the pantry with ample storage space. Upstairs there are the bedrooms, you won't be disappointed in the size of the primary bedroom and bathroom. This unit has a enclosed screen patio and no rear neighbors. Great property for family and pets with an awesome park just steps away from the property.
